regressions:
Bug: 299570702
Bug: 299561281

Test: Test: m com.android.btservices
Test: QA validation
Ignore-AOSP-First: security
(cherry picked from https://googleplex-android-review.googlesource.com/q/commit:778d3fb3fb520e54425ecefe9a28453002053553)
